If you are looking for a beautiful apartment in an area that has nearly everything you could ask for, this one bedroom flat in the wonderful Piedmont Avenue neighborhood is now available.  This apartment's layout makes a super one-bedroom arrangement but works equally well as a two bedroom if you don't require a huge living room.  Located in the heart of Piedmont Avenue near the theater, this apartment, located in a Linda Avenue 4-plex, has it all, including: 
Hardwood floors (not laminate) throughout;
White wooden blind window coverings throughout;
Appliances including gas range and built-in overhead microwave, dishwasher and refrigerator; 
Washer and dryer in unit;
Granite kitchen countertops;
Nicely tiled shower/tub;
STORAGE - both the bedroom and the front room have huge closets, plus there is a linen closet;
Piedmont Avenue restaurants, dry cleaners, grocery store, theater, Starbucks, Peats, hairdressers, banks, and Kaiser Hospital are all within a short walk.  The free Kaiser Bart shuttle, running between the Oakland Medical Center and MacArthur Bart, is a six block walk.   
Off-street parking is available.  
